data.meta_description: Just uploaded some of our latest 11th Street Bridge Park renderings to our website. Check them out & let us know what you think! https://bbardc.org/park/
data.text: As Parks and Recreation Month comes to an end, we want to celebrate along with our amazing partners at the DC Department of Parks and Recreation and our wonderful collaborators at the National Park Service East. Together, we are so excited to celebrate Parks and Recreation Month by highlighting our efforts to help bring the 11th Street Bridge Park to life. This community civic space, located on the piers of the old 11th Street Bridge, will be a space for healthy recreation, environmental education, and the art #dcbridgepark #parkandrecreationmonth #parkandrecreationmonth2024
